<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式名稱：香港之路 The Hong Kong Way<br />\n日期：２０１９年８月２３日（星期五）<br />\n集合地點：港島線及荃灣觀塘線沿線各港鐵站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路線圖 (細節待定)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOnPTuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOnPTuT.jpg&h=f65321a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大致分三段：<br />\n港島線（筲箕灣 &mdash; 堅尼地城）：13KM<br />\n荃灣線（黃埔 &mdash; 美孚）：7.02KM<br />\n觀塘線（深水埗 &mdash; 油塘）：12.6KM<br />\n<br />\n時序：<br />\n集合並在行人路上排隊 19:15-20:00<br />\n手牽手組人鏈 20:00-21:00<br />\n和平散去 21:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">快啲幫手開post宣傳<br />\n 整文宣！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d47ff45752c34537cddf68d97e368b3b84a4e92","tid":1486412,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dd56acf2e2bc012d4ce84dc9acd50df105489cb","tid":1486412,"uid":257422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://g2.dcdn.lt/images/pix/baltijos-kelias-v-cepliausko-nuotr-65429744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg2.dcdn.lt%2Fimages%2Fpix%2Fbaltijos-kelias-v-cepliausko-nuotr-65429744.jpg&h=6678ec11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">8月23日 人鏈：香港之路Hong Kong Way正！式！上！線！！！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih